metadata.editComments: Another rare Gwen song aside from "U Started It", but instead of sectional key changes, the post-chorus uses what could be a D# Bebop Major derivative mode starting on g#m (except for the f#m chord which is merely borrowed) according to a chord compatibility calculator xD; but the tonic in almost the whole song is clearly g#m. But any fix of chord labels is welcome.
First song by GS in Locrian (although it's only the outro part) lol.
